{
  "id": "adv_card_ai_05_01_short",
  "title": "小美山愛 1話 一人だけゼロ回 (Short)",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_01-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、今回の沖縄合宿は\n本っっっ当っっにお手数をおかけします！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ I apologize for causing\nso much trouble with this Okinawa training camp!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 7.8324490547
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_01-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "このご恩は、小美山愛、一生を懸けて\n必ずお返しいたしますから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll definitely repay this favor‚\nAi Komiyama‚ with all my heart!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.7700779756,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 14.2338093758
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "そんなにかしこまらなくていいよ\n俺のことは気にせず合宿に集中してくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You don't need to be so formal.\nJust focus on the training camp‚ don't worry about me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.8072126042,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "こころから聞いていると思うけど\n俺は、莉央さんと葵に内緒でこっそりついて行くよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sure Kokoro told you‚\nbut I'll secretly follow without Rio-san and Aoi knowing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.3881580604,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 26.1338093758
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_01-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "これまた本当に申し訳ありません……\n{user}さんのこと、邪魔者みたいに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm really sorry about that too…\nFeeling like I'm intruding on {user}-san…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.555219836,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_01-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "私はもちろん、こころだって\n本心ではそんな風には思ってないんですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course‚ that's not how I truly feel‚\nneither for Kokoro.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.6900524958,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 39.6442851068
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "新曲作りはもちろんだけど\n莉央さん達と夏を楽しむのも、合宿の目的なんだろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I know the main purpose of the camp is to work on the new song‚\nbut also to have fun with Rio-san and Aoi during summer.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.7425490063,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "俺がついて行くと\nどうしても仕事中心っぽくなるしな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If I'm around‚\nit will inevitably become work-centered.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 49.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_01-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "そう言っていただけると、少し気が楽になります",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So hearing that from you puts my mind at ease.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_05_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "でも、何かトラブルがあったら表に出て行くからな\nアイドルを守るのが俺の仕事だから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But if any trouble arises‚ I'll step forward to handle it.\nIt's my job to protect the idols.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.4,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}